---
---

<section class="exec-section exec-hero" id="exec-hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img src="/branding-identity/backgrounds/hero-background.png" alt="" class="hero-bg-img" />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-logo">
      <img src="/branding-identity/patientOS.png" alt="Machina" class="hero-logo-img" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-badge">Executive Briefing</div>
    <h1>What if half your <em>operational workforce</em> never clocked in, never burned out, and never <span class="teal">dropped a patient?</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Machina deploys an agentic AI workforce alongside your human team. The result: your people operate at maximum efficiency, patients stop falling through cracks, and your overhead stays as small as possible.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exec-hero {
    text-align: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.65);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 120px 40px 100px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    animation: execFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.1s both;
  }

  .hero-logo-img {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(240,180,41,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(240,180,41,0.2);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 8px 22px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 44px;
    animation: execFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
  }

  .exec-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5.8vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 940px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    animation: execFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s both;
  }

  .exec-hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .exec-hero h1 .teal {
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--gray-300);
    max-width: 660px;
    margin: 0 auto 52px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    animation: execFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.6s both;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 28px;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    animation: execFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.8s both;
  }

  .scroll-cue {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    animation: execFadeUp 0.8s ease 1s both;
  }

  .scroll-cue span {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  .scroll-arrow {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-right: 1.5px solid var(--gray-500);
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--gray-500);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    animation: execBounce 2s infinite;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-content {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .exec-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
